{"word":"προσφθέγγομαι","slug":"προσφθέγγομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσφθέγγομαι</b></el> <el>(doric <el>ποτι-φθ</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to call to, address, accost, salute</i>, <el>τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to call by a name, call</i> so and so, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}